            <title>实试 Sony FE 50-150mm F2 GM  人像半身 Close Up 至全身一支镜头完全覆盖</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 22 Apr 2025 14:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相机测试]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304556</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 今日正式发布全新镜头 FE 50-150mm F2 GM，属于全球首款具备恒定 F2.0 大光圈的中远摄变焦镜头 ，属于 G Master 系列最新旗舰之作。我们 unwire 记者早前就到了发布会会场，亲自试用这支极具份量的大光圈新镜头。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304557" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609-694x508.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="508" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609-694x508.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002609.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304558" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002618.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC04297" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468849118/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468849118_74336c18d8_b.jpg" alt="DSC04297" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04259" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468848073/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468848073_a1cf7c9114_b.jpg" alt="DSC04259" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>点击<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/albums/72177720325319072/">此连结</a>看今次试相</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1304578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-694x541.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="541" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-694x541.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250422105444-scaled.jpg 1154w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>全球首款 50-150mm F2 恒定光圈变焦镜头</h2><p>Sony FE 50-150mm F2 GM 是首支横跨 50mm 至 150mm 焦段、并具备恒定 F2 光圈的远摄变焦镜头，专为新世代影像创作者设计，涵盖人像、婚礼、体育等多样拍摄场景。无论在 50mm 广角端拍摄婚礼场景，还是在 150mm 端捕捉运动瞬间，都可呈现细腻清晰的主体与柔和自然的散景。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626-528x580.jpg" alt="" width="528" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626-528x580.jpg 528w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002626.jpg 819w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 528px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC04285" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468782784/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468782784_1d831726f6_b.jpg" alt="DSC04285" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04351" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940820/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940820_6fc7222633_b.jpg" alt="DSC04351" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04323" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468848633/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468848633_3e1779189c_b.jpg" alt="DSC04323" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04360" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54467748612/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54467748612_19a051b313_b.jpg" alt="DSC04360" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>光学设计与解析力表现</h2><p>镜头采用 17 组 19 片光学结构，包含 2 片 XA 极致非球面镜片、2 片非球面镜片、2 片 Super ED 超低色散镜片，以及 3 片 ED 低色散镜片，强效抑制色差，提升画质。加上 Sony 独家 Nano AR 纳米镀膜 II，能有效减少炫光和鬼影，即使在强烈逆光环境下也能保有清晰对比。</p><p>根据 Sony 内部测试，这支镜头在最大光圈 F2 下，无论是 50mm 还是 150mm，从画面中央到边缘都维持极高解像度与对比度，媲美定焦镜的光学品质。</p><p><a title="DSC04269" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54467749442/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54467749442_d373d9c7c2_b.jpg" alt="DSC04269" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>散景效果柔和自然</h2><p>FE 50-150mm F2 GM 配备 11 片圆形光圈叶片，营造顺滑柔和的背景虚化效果，减少洋葱圈纹理，呈现干净细腻的散景，完美衬托主体。无论是人像的眼神交流，或是动作瞬间，都赋予影像更好的层次感。</p><p><a title="DSC04450" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940085/in/album-72177720325319072" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940085_b5a18fb692_b.jpg" alt="DSC04450" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04408" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468587276/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468587276_fe59d8772b_b.jpg" alt="DSC04408" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04262" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940270/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940270_c3d3e86210_b.jpg" alt="DSC04262" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04445" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468783054/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468783054_680d6b7f09_b.jpg" alt="DSC04445" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04410" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468941120/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468941120_64b44397c1_b.jpg" alt="DSC04410" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>灵活稳定的手持拍摄体验</h2><p>镜头采用内变焦设计，长时间拍摄时，无需担心镜头重心改变影响平衡感。整体尺寸为 102.8mm × 200mm，重量约 1340 克（不含脚架座），适合各类手持拍摄场合。相比同为远摄变焦的 FE 70-200mm F2.8 GM OSS II，FE 50-150mm F2 GM 提供更大光圈与更灵活的焦段选择。虽然镜身足有 1340 克，但对于日常工作例如婚摄工作者来说，这支镜头可在不同焦段都有 F2 光圈，灵活拍摄之余也能获得极为柔和散景，只要工作能顺利完成，这支镜头的重量实在并非太大负担。</p><h2>对焦性能卓越，捕捉精彩瞬间</h2><p>镜头搭载 4 组 XD 线性马达，配合浮动对焦结构，FE 50-150mm F2 GM 实现高效静音对焦，迅速锁定快速移动的主体，无论是运动赛事还是野生动物皆能轻松掌握。特别是在搭配 α9 III 机身时，可发挥高达 120 fps 连拍性能，完美捕捉每一瞬间。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc04360.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p><a title="DSC04372" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468782084/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468782084_4c90ab4211_b.jpg" alt="DSC04372" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04366" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468940495/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468940495_151bf6d3de_b.jpg" alt="DSC04366" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04416" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468941360/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468941360_1df5d934f8_b.jpg" alt="DSC04416" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC04326" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54468849028/in/album-72177720325319072/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54468849028_f4c854cb3b_b.jpg" alt="DSC04326" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>影片拍摄特化设计</h2><p>为影片创作者而设，FE 50-150mm F2 GM 内建多项针对影片拍摄增强功能。镜头设计有效抑制呼吸效应，实现自然流畅的焦点转移，配合 Alpha 机身的呼吸补偿，拍摄时更显细腻。内变焦与平衡设计，便于安装于稳定器（gimbal），提升动态拍摄灵活性。</p><h2>操控性与细节设计</h2><p>镜头配置专业级操控按钮与环节，包括三个可自订对焦固定按钮、全时 DMF 切换、光圈环与无段式光圈切换、变焦环及对焦环，提供灵活直观操作。全新设计的遮光罩支援滤镜转接，脚架座亦可快速拆卸，符合专业使用需求。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625-694x430.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="430" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625-694x430.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002625.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002628.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632-694x377.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/l1002632.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">与 FE 28-70mm F2 GM （图上左方）比较</p><h2>定价与上市资讯</h2><p>FE 50-150mm F2 GM 建议售价为 HKD 27,990，预售日期自 4 月 23 日至 4 月 27 日，透过 Sony Online Store、专门店及特约零售商进行预购，预计 4 月 29 日起正式取货。预售期间加送 G 系列 TOUGH 规格 SD 卡（SF-G128T），价值 HKD 1,640。</p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/22/sony-fe-50-150mm-f2-gm/dc/">实试 Sony FE 50-150mm F2 GM  人像半身 Close Up 至全身一支镜头完全覆盖</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
