                <![CDATA[<p>以往 iOS 要将录音变成文字稿的话，需下载第三方应用程式，而程式质素良莠不齐，部分免费程式设有限额，收费程式价格普遍昂贵，而且部分用户也许会担心资讯安全问题。今日小编想和大家分享 iOS 内置的语音备忘录转文字稿功能，可以将录音快速变成文字，而且不用担心资料外泄。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ga-535x580.png" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ga-535x580.png 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ga.png 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲录音一键变文字稿，支援广东话！</p><h2>需求</h2><p>iPhone 12 或更新机款</p><p>iOS 18.4 或更新版本</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0435-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0435-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_0435.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更新 iOS 18.4 后首次开启原生「录音机」会看见上面画面，显示可使用「转写纪录」功能</p><h2>Step 1 开启内置「录音机」</h2><p>要使用录音转文字功能，首先你要开启内置「录音机」App，然后开始录音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_1739-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_1739-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_1739.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启录音机</p><p>现在你可以点击红色键录音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8019-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8019-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8019.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲然后开始录音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8020-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8020-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8020.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲录完音就可以点击停止键</p><br /><b>
